Arms wave overhead with sine wave
Big smile on face
Stars/confetti burst particles
Transitions to IDLE after celebration ends, then reveals UI

5. STATE: IDLE

Gentle up-down bob using Math.sin(idlePhase) * 3.5
Slow arm sway
Slight lean oscillation
Pupils follow mouse cursor position (eyes track the mouse)
Breathing squash (very subtle scale oscillation)


